{"name":"Push Through","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-flame-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Auxiliary<br />Action: Counter<br />Prerequisites: None<br />Range: None<br />Targets: Self<br />Trigger: You would otherwise hit 0 HP<br />Cost: None (but see Special)</p><p>Effect: Note how much damage beyond 0 HP the triggering damage would do, referred to as the overkill damage. Make an Endure check with a target of 10 + the overkill damage. On success, you instead fall to 1 HP.<br />Special: You roll on the Injury Type Table when you use this Ability. If you fail the Endure check, you roll a second Injury. Injuries take effect after the Endure check.<br />Description: Pushing through otherwise disabling damage, at risk of significant further harm if the strain is too much. This can be gritty determination, a state of focus that trancends pain, emergency stimulants, or similar measures.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"counter","cost":0,"condition":"You would otherwise hit 0 HP"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"none"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.oeWAGeTqMbBzwMZS"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.9.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683010448090,"modifiedTime":1683010614930,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3},"_id":"0M1MdCgt8kNhCv9w"}
