{"name":"Shocking Bolt","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-creature-pink.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: If this Ability hits, the target becomes Shocked for two rounds. The Shock severity is equal to your Hero Tier.<br />Description: Anything that does lingering sky damage. This can be a thunder incantation, rattling a foe with sonic force, a lightning ray, or similar effects.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":2,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":10},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x2 (Sky)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Elemental Lance & Sky Attunement"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668820621871,"modifiedTime":1670974925193,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"4j6pf1iiYpcg5xWu","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Elemental Strike","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-purple.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x2 (Fire/Ice/Earth/Sky/Light/Dark)<br />Effect: You may only use an element that you have taken the corresponding Elemental Attunement for.<br />This Attack targets the enemy's Mental Defense rather than Physical Defense.<br />Description: Channeling elemental energy into a melee strike. This could be igniting one's hands with fire, swinging an ice sword, lightning kicks, and similar elemental attacks.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"hp","target":"attributes.hp.value","amount":7},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x2 (Fire/Ice/Earth/Sky/Light/Dark)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Elemental Attunement"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668819461339,"modifiedTime":1670974925170,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"6AqFwJoP1C6KylET","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Leyline","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/lightning/barrier-shield-crackling-orb-pink.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: While standing in the affected Square, you (and only you) increase your Offense or Defense stats by an amount equal to your Hero Tier, chosen when you first cast this Ability.<br />You cannot cast Leyline again while a previous Leyline you cast is still active.<br />Intelligent enemies can easily recognize Leylines and understand their implications.<br />Description: Augmenting a location to lend you power. This can be tapping into currents of power flowing through an area, setting up a device that projects an empowering field, invoking the spirits of the dead to empower you at a given place, and other similar effects.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":null,"amount":1},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":8},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668819864474,"modifiedTime":1670974925177,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"7v5nIYEn8eaeq3kZ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
