{"name":"Crushing Demand","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/shield-damaged-broken-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x1 (Physical)<br />Effect: You may uses your Physical Offense or you Mental Offense on this Ability. If you use Physical Offense, treat this Ability and an Attack. If you use Mental Offense, treat this Ability as a Spell.<br />On hit, this Ability also Provokes its target.<br />You may choose to use your Defense Bonus instead of your Offense for this Ability.<br />Scaling: You may increase the cost of this Ability by 6 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1.<br />Description: You overwhelm a foes defenses using your own. This could reflect a shield bash, striking with armored limbs, overloading your mechanical armor's energy shields, or similar techniques which rely on armor.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Demand"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668471414546,"modifiedTime":1670974925167,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"98m6sjzaXYfRjWLV","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Blood Lance","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-helix-blood-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x2 (Physical)<br />Effect: This Spell targets the opponent's Physical Defense rather than Mental Defense. If you increase the cost by 4 HP, you may use this Ability at Medium Range.<br />Description: A powerful and unusual short-ranged Spell, which can be used from a greater distance at greater cost. This could be channeling blood magic, diverting energy to weapons for a powerful strike, charging a weapon with spiritual power, or something similar.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"short"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"hp","target":"attributes.hp.value","amount":9},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x2 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668471121019,"modifiedTime":1670974925155,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"9pJlESNJTzCrnz26","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
