{"name":"Doom","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-glow.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: If you hit with this Spell, the target decreases on The Offensive Track or The Defensive Track, your choice. When you pay the Upkeep cost, you must repeat the Magic Offense roll against the target: if you miss, this Spell immediately ends (though the damage done to the victim’s buff tracks remains until otherwise reversed). If you hit, the Spell repeats. If you choose to maintain Doom, you must use the same buff/debuff track as the one first selected. If you wish to target a different track, you must start a new Doom casting.<br />You may only have one instance of Doom at a time; if you wish to switch to a different target or track, you must re-cast Doom. (Exception: If you have the Cascading Curses Talent, you may have two instances of Doom active.)<br />Description: You cause the victim to gradually become weaker. This can be inflicting a curse that drains the target’s energy over time, coating the target with nanobots or a chemical substance that inhibits their bodies, invoking vengeful spirits drag the target down, or similar effects.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":null,"amount":2},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":8},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: 0","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Enfeeble&Expose"},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.eUBy8DuNtivJtFpl"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0